Company Overview of American Realty Capital - Retail Centers of America, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
American Realty Capital - Retail Centers of America, Inc. is a privately owned real estate estate investment trust. It invests in the real state markets of United States. The firm primarily invests in the retail properties including lifestyle centers, power centers and large needs-based shopping centers. American Realty Capital - Retail Centers of America, Inc. was formed on July 29, 2010 and is based in New York, New York.


